"Yeah, hold on a nano."  She pressed a few buttons and a sheet with 
the cordanants on it printed up.  she tore the sheet from the printer 
and handed it to Quickstrike. "Hear you go. This will point him in 
the right direction."  She thought a moment. "If he was in 
Hellbeast's group, what make him loyal to us? Won't he turn on us 
like he did with Hellbeast?"
